name: Kensington Hi-Fi Headphones with Mic - Headset - on-ear - wired - 3.5 mm jack - black | Dell USA

Supporting common core learning standards, the headphones provide a max output of 94db for safe listening and the mic supports the latest audio-based classroom testing requirements. The Hi-Fi Headphones with Microphone is suitable for students, call centers, business professionals, and recreational gamers. Compatible with Windows, Mac, and Chromebook for a simple plug and play experience.
